Create a hasura project (dashboard.hasura.io and then activate the free trial project)
You'll get a projectname of the type: someword45
Download hasuractl
hasuractl login
hasuractl set-context someword45
hasuractl add-ssh-key
hasuractl quickstart r-shiny app --create
Your R files will be inside app/myapp/. You can change the Server.R and ui.R files. You can add any more files that you need.
git commit and then git push hasura master and your app will go live on app.someword42.hasura-app.io

